title: Krempels King of the Road Challenge
description: The Krempels King of the Road Challenge is a fundraising event for the Krempels Center, a Portsmouth NH based nonprofit organization dedicated to improving the lives of people living with brain injury from trauma, tumor or stroke.
course: Three routes are available 10 miles, 50K (30 miles) and 100K (62 miles).
